title: RQ: VA Easy Pop - Hello World (Dutch Treat _A128 MAD HQ)
description:
On request: a playlist from the MAD (Music Against Depression) project, with `stay the night` and `whisper` from Fine Frenzy. Ok? If you try to download a member and it is not running (because people do not share) or you just looking for some music, all individual playlists are available in the Dutch Treat collection Updates.

Numbers beginning beginning with a ^ are temporary and beginning with an _ definitive. `A` stands for Various artists and various styles. `B` for one artist, `C` for my personal Sweetlists and `I` for Indie.... Enjoy,
